'''''Behind the Curtain, Pleasantries and Secrets''''' is an [[Adventure Mission]] on [[Astral Express]] in the chapter [[As Tomorrow Became Yesterday]].

==Steps==
# Access Boothill and "Rappa's" Memory Bubble
# Access the Memory Bubble of Himeko's communications with the Strategic Investment Department
# Access the Memory Bubble of Himeko's communications with the Xianzhou Luofu
# Access the Memory Bubble of Himeko's communications with the Galaxy Rangers

